title: Everyone You Admire Was Once a Fraud, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO54
description: As you pursue greatness, do you ever feel like a fraud?  Do you even feel like, deep down, maybe everyone thinks you're someone that you're not?  Don't sweat it. Everyone who has ever accomplished anything has wrestled with the same thing, too.
